The '''''SkyWind III''''' was an [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaanian]] diplomatic vessel that operated during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was [[Attack on SkyWind III|attacked]] by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] [[Destroyer/Legends|destroyer]] ''[[Starshot]]'', in an attempt to capture the ''SkyWind III''{{'s}} passenger, [[Ambassador/Legends|Ambassador]] [[Lerron]].

